				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$\mbox{few} \times 1/64\mbox{ s}$\end{document}). If the range format is set to “automatic”, then the following algorithm operates and the “manual” range bits are ignored.

