Known in each CHU frame are the vectors Xref and Yref. To establish the Zref axis it is noted that Xref and Yref spans a plane the normal of which is the natural choice for Zref. 
				Zref=Xref×Yref/norm(Xref×Yref)\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
